Subject: error setting profile connection to GMSA account
Description: We are trying to set the profile connection to use GMSA account.  The account is already running SQL services on the server so it is configured correctly at the server level.  We get a permissions error and have checked and it has full control on stealthaudit folders.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Access Denied error when trying to add the gMSA to the connection profile

[Resolution]
The account used to run NEA (and being used to add the gMSA to the console) must have permissions to access the gMSA password
